    "P8: I think that this method ensures that we have all the responsibility in the learning process and that it is a student-centered education process.",
    "In addition, when the participants were asked how online flipped learning supported by Metaverse-based technology contributed to learning medical English regarding language skills, a great majority of the participants (N = 8) stated that it was helpful to improve their reading skills whereas five students reported that it was useful to learn vocabulary.",
